name: Peanut
description: In loving memory of Peanut the Squirrel, taken from us prematurely. Though his tiny heart no longer beats, his spirit endures through $PNUT on Ethereum. Now a beacon of community power, with no singular developer at the helm, this token stands as a tribute to Peanut's indomitable essence. His playful antics and acrobatic feats are immortalized in the decentralized ledger, a testament to his lasting impact. $PNUT is not just a token; it's a movement, a collective vow to keep Peanut's legacy scampering through the digital forests of the blockchain. Forever in our hearts, forever in the memepool.
